primary_asset_contracts.description:
ACTUAL HOLDER COUNT AS OF 2/3/2022: 4941. 45% STAKED IN YOH FARMING

8,888 hand-drawn trading cards + NFT powered 'play to earn' game, inspired by ancient Japanese mythology. 

By international artist Geo Law (clients inc' Walt Disney, Google, Facebook, NYTimes, Sumo Digital game studio, etc). 

Each genesis launch hero card is based on Oni (鬼), a fearsome yōkai spirit, and will be the key to unlock the Yokai Kingdom metaverse, including the play-to-earn game Oni’s Quest.
